rithmetic\",\n        \"definition of modular arithmetic\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"claim\": \"(2000 + 2001 + 2002 + 2003 + 2004 + 2005 + 2006) % 7 = 0.\",\n      \"reasoning\": \"Combining step 3 and step 4 gives the desired result.\",\n      \"facts_used\": [\n        \"step 3\",\n        \"step 4\"\n      ]\n    }\n  ],\n  \"final_answer\": \"0\"\n}\n\nProduce the JSON formalization."
